{
  "id": "campaign_guides/legacy_of_the_ancestors/83_ren_kobo_merchant_loa/83_3_loa",
  "lookup_group": "campaign_guides/legacy_of_the_ancestors",
  "lookup_id": "83.3",
  "title": "83.3 (LOA)",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The man\u2019s familiar, broad face has been weathered by years of strong wind, and his eyes are surrounded by a forest of wrinkles from a lifetime of squinting into the sun. He pulls his hand out of the pocket of his long coat and thrusts it forward."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "He speaks with the drawl of the Messipian seafolk. \u201cAlways good to see a Ranger,\u201d he says. \u201cPerhaps you\u2019d like to make a trade?\u201d"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "em",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "span",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Clear Ren Kobo with"
                },
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "items": [
                    {
                      "type": "icon",
                      "icon": "progress",
                      "color": "black"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "to trade with him."
                }
              ],
              "color": "blue"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "His smile broadens. \u201cAlso, perhaps I can interest you in attending the swap meet at my market? People are coming from all over the Valley to trade items of great significance. I\u2019m sure you\u2019d find it incredibly beneficial\u2014both spiritually and commercially! I\u2019m on my way to the market now. You should join me! The journey is always more pleasurable when shared with a friend. Don\u2019t you agree?\u201d"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Gain the"
        },
        {
          "type": "b",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "LIMITED TIME OFFER"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "mission. Write 199.1 three days from now on the day tracker."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "em",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "span",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Travel to Kobo\u2019s Market to participate in the swap meet. There you\u2019ll have the opportunity to gain some of the reward cards you may have missed from the Lure of the Valley campaign."
                }
              ],
              "color": "blue"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
